# Air-gap-authoritative AND source for the version matrix (P3-IMG.2).
#
# Copy to bootimage/supported-versions and list the OCP versions THIS environment
# has MIRRORED / can actually install (the truly-installable set). The boot-image
# matrix is intersected with this — so CAPA only bakes images for versions a
# cluster can really be here, not every version the SaaS offers.
#
# When present, detect uses this by default (no --ai-versions needed). Pre-release
# (-ec/-rc/-fc) lines are ignored unless --include-prereleases. minors only matter.
4.20.22
